text.tspan: Distribution of democratic features weighted by population, 2021
Based on the expert assessments and index by the Bertelsmann Transformation Index (2022). It combines
information on the extent of political participation, the rule of law, stable democratic institutions, political and social
integration, and a capable state. It ranges from 1 to 10 (most democratic).
Source: Bertelsmann Transformation Index (2022), Gapminder (v6), HYDE (v3.2), UN (2019)
